{"type":null,"faqId":46215,"title":"为何双击屏幕未唤醒屏幕？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.38402778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>请先确认“设置”—“手势控制”—“双击屏幕唤醒”开关是否打开，如打开再确定操作是否在规格范围内：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、  </span><span>在屏幕边缘范围1cm之内是不识别的。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、  </span><span>两次点击的时间不能超过500ms。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3、  </span><span>两次点击的距离不超过5mm。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4、  </span><span>不要在锁屏之后立马进行相关操作。灭屏800ms之后才能识别您的动作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5、  </span><span>双击的时候是否遮挡了接近光孔，如果挡住接近光孔，是不识别的。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1995","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376340000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":69,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"双击屏幕,唤醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}